    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute favorite ride. She\u2019s in really great shape and has been so reliable for me\u2014honestly, a total gem to drive! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with everything so she\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today. If you\u2019re looking for a solid, well-loved car that won't let you down, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
