    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies for exceptional transient throttle response. The power is sent to the rear wheels via a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a mechanical limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its signature balance, featuring reinforced subframe mounts and refreshed suspension bushings to ensure structural rigidity. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the double VANOS system is quiet and the valvetrain remains precisely calibrated. This is a mechanically sound example that delivers a linear power band and visceral feedback all the way to its 8,000 RPM redline.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
