    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies engineering excellence and sophisticated design. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure optimal mechanical performance and structural integrity. The interior cabin reflects a high standard of care, while the exterior maintains its professional finish. With a verified service history and a focus on long-term reliability, this selection offers a refined driving experience for the discerning professional seeking a balance of luxury and value.",
      "price": 34900.0,
