    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next road trip? I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this car, and it\u2019s served me so well. It\u2019s in solid shape, drives smoothly, and has plenty of life left in it! It\u2019s been well-cared for and is just waiting for someone new to take the wheel. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 31500.0,
